Detailed Description

cvmx_zip_que::_ecc_err_sta

ZIP_QUEX_ECC_ERR_STA = ZIP Queue ECC ERROR STATUS Register

Description: This register contains the first ECC SBE/DBE status for the instruction buffer of a given zip instruction queue.
